<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>T001-0001287 · Guía De Remisión Electrónica</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; }
  :root {
    --ink: #1a2720;
    --ink-2: #48554e;
    --ink-3: #7b8882;
    --accent: #1d6b4f;
    --accent-2: #d1e7dc;
    --accent-soft: #f2f8f5;
    --line: #d9e0dc;
    --paper: #fdfdfb;
  }
  body {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    width: 219px;
    min-height: auto;
    padding: 10px;
    min-height: 1123px;
    padding: 40px 44px;
  }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  p, h1, h2, h3, h4 { margin: 0; }

  .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; align-items: start; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .brand .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
  .brand .logo { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .brand .logo svg { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
  .brand .co-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .brand .co-tagline { font-size: 8px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 1px; }
  .brand .meta { margin-top: 14px; font-size: 8px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .brand .meta p { padding: 1px 0; }

  .doc-id { text-align: right; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 18px; min-width: 240px; }
  .doc-id .tag { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .doc-id .kind { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 4px; }
  .doc-id .num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--accent); margin-top: 2px; }
  .doc-id .ruc { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .doc-id .ruc b { color: var(--ink); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
  .doc-id .issued { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-2); }

  .meta-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .meta-row .chip { background: var(--accent-soft); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 12px; }
  .meta-row .chip .k { font-size: 9px; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .meta-row .chip .v { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; }

  .parties { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .party { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; }
  .party .label { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--ink-3); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .party .name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .party .row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 1fr; font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 0; }
  .party .row .k { color: var(--ink-3); }

  .section-title { font-size: 9.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 10px; }

  .items-wrap { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  .items thead th { font-size: 9.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; text-align: left; padding: 12px 12px; background: var(--accent-soft); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .items tbody td { padding: 11px 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; font-size: 8px; }
  .items .c-idx { width: 26px; color: var(--ink-3); text-align: center; }
  .items .c-code { width: 90px; }
  .items .c-qty, .items .c-price, .items .c-tax { text-align: right; }
  .items .c-qty { width: 60px; }
  .items .c-unit { width: 48px; text-align: center; color: var(--ink-3); }
  .items .c-price { width: 84px; }
  .items .c-tax { width: 86px; }
  .items .desc .main { font-weight: 500; }
  .items .desc .sub { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 2px; }

  .bottom { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 20px; margin-top: 18px; }
  .notes .block { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .notes .block .head { font-size: 9.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .notes .block .body { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink); }
  .notes .block .body p + p { margin-top: 2px; }
  .notes .small { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); }

  .totals { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .totals .inner { padding: 14px 18px; }
  .totals .line { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 4px 0; font-size: 8px; }
  .totals .line .k { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .totals .line .v { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; white-space: nowrap; }
  .totals .rule { border-top: 1px dashed var(--line); margin: 6px 0; }
  .totals .grand-wrap { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 14px 18px; }
  .totals .grand { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; }
  .totals .grand .k { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0.85; }
  .totals .grand .v { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; }
  .totals .grand-wrap .words { font-size: 9.5px; margin-top: 6px; opacity: 0.85; }

  .foot { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr auto; gap: 18px; align-items: start; margin-top: 22px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .foot .qr { width: 110px; height: 110px; background: #fff; padding: 6px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .foot .qr svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
  .foot .meta { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .foot .meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .foot .meta .hash { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; word-break: break-all; font-size: 8.5px; margin-top: 4px; color: var(--ink-3); }
  .foot .stamp { text-align: right; min-width: 180px; }
  .foot .stamp .badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; background: var(--accent-2); color: var(--accent); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .foot .stamp .badge::before { content: ""; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; }
  .foot .stamp .line { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 8px; max-width: 180px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="brand">
    <div class="mark">
      <div class="logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.4">
          <rect x="6" y="6" width="28" height="28" rx="3"/>
          <path d="M12 20h16M12 14h10M12 26h14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="co-name">Manufacturas Andina Textil S.A.C.</div>
        <div class="co-tagline">Hilando lo mejor de los Andes desde 2001</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta">
      <p>{{ doc.company.address.direccion }} — Lima, Perú</p>
      <p>ventas@andinatextil.pe · (01) 555-0102 · andinatextil.pe</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="doc-id">
    <div class="tag">Comprobante</div>
    <div class="kind">Guía De Remisión Electrónica</div>
    <div class="num">T001-0001287</div>
    <div class="ruc">RUC <b>{{ doc.company.ruc }}</b></div>
    <div class="issued">Emitido {{ doc.fechaEmision|date('d/m/Y') }} · 14:32</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="meta-row">
  <div class="chip"><span class="k">Moneda</span><span class="v">Soles ({{ moneda }})</span></div>
  <div class="chip"><span class="k">T/C</span><span class="v mono">3.742</span></div>
  <div class="chip"><span class="k">Vencimiento</span><span class="v">24/05/2026</span></div>
  <div class="chip"><span class="k">Condición</span><span class="v">Crédito 2 cuotas</span></div>
</div>

<div class="parties">
  <div class="party">
    <div class="label">Cliente</div>
    <div class="name">Comercial Los Portales S.A.</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">RUC</span><span class="mono">{{ cl.numDoc }}</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Dirección</span><span>{{ cl.address.direccion }}</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Ubicación</span><span>Lima — Lima — Miraflores</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">O/C</span><span class="mono">OC-2026-00487</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="party">
    <div class="label">Operación</div>
    <div class="name">0101 — Venta interna</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Entrega</span><span>Almacén Los Portales · Callao</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Guía</span><span class="mono">GRE T001-00452</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Vendedor</span><span>Diego Paredes</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Ruta</span><span>Lima–Callao</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p class="section-title">Detalle del comprobante</p>
<div class="items-wrap">
<table class="items">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th class="c-idx">#</th>
      <th class="c-code">Código</th>
      <th>Descripción</th>
      <th class="c-unit">Und</th>
      <th class="c-qty">Cant.</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>

    {% for det in doc.details %}
    <tr>
      <td class="c-idx mono">{{ loop.index|str_pad(2, '0', 'left') }}</td>
      <td class="c-code mono">{{ det.codigo }}</td>
      <td class="desc"><div class="main">{{ det.descripcion }}</div></td>
      <td class="c-unit">{{ det.unidad }}</td>
      <td class="c-qty mono">{{ det.cantidad }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="foot">
  <div class="qr">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 21 21" shape-rendering="crispEdges"><rect width="21" height="21" fill="#fff"/>
    <g fill="#1d6b4f">
      <rect x="0" y="0" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="1" y="1" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="2" y="2" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="14" y="0" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="15" y="1" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="16" y="2" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="0" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="1" y="15" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="2" y="16" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="8" y="0" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="10" y="0" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="12" y="2" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="5" y="8" width="2" height="2"/><rect x="8" y="8" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="8" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="13" y="8" width="3" height="1"/><rect x="17" y="8" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="19" y="8" width="2" height="1"/>
      <rect x="1" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="4" y="10" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="6" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="9" y="10" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="12" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="15" y="10" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="18" y="10" width="2" height="1"/>
      <rect x="0" y="12" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="3" y="12" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="6" y="12" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="8" y="12" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="12" width="2" height="2"/><rect x="17" y="12" width="2" height="2"/>
      <rect x="8" y="14" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="10" y="14" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="13" y="14" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="15" y="14" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="18" y="14" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="8" y="16" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="16" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="14" y="16" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="17" y="16" width="1" height="1"/>
      <rect x="9" y="18" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="12" y="18" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="15" y="18" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="17" y="18" width="2" height="1"/>
      <rect x="8" y="20" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="20" width="3" height="1"/><rect x="15" y="20" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="18" y="20" width="1" height="1"/>
    </g></svg>
  </div>
  <div class="meta">
    <p><strong>Representación impresa</strong> de la Guía De Remisión Electrónica.</p>
    <p>Consulte la validez de este documento en <strong>sunat.gob.pe</strong> con el RUC del emisor y el número del comprobante.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:6px;">Firmante: {{ doc.company.ruc }} · Manufacturas Andina Textil S.A.C.</p>
    <p class="hash">Hash SHA1: 3f8a21bc9d7e04a6c2f1b8e0d4a7c9f2e5b6d8a1</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stamp">
    <span class="badge">CPE autorizado</span>
    <div class="line">Emitido conforme al Reglamento de Comprobantes de Pago SUNAT.</div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
